description.narrative: (Ethiopia): This mechanism will support and field evaluate an automated malaria rapid diagnostic test (RDT) reader (Deki reader) and data management device for P.falciparum and P.vivax malaria in selected locations in Ethiopia. The RDT reader is a very effective and useful tool in low to moderate malaria countries including elimination settings in case investigation, follow-up and response activities. .The activities will include: .Development of the assessment protocol and tools.Training of field assessment teams and conduct the assessment in selected locations.Analysis and prepare the assessment report.Dissemination of the assessment findings..
